snippet.description:
With DCP Chitrole now having joined forces with Marco, the whole team CID is left bewildered. As Marco and Chitrole plot to kill the CID inspectors who had gathered in a mall, Sachin and Kavin try to collect some information from witnesses. This eventually leads to Marco being arrested, but a bigger hand is discovered to be in play. Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya

‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #sonypal #cid2023 #latestcid #cidfullepisode 

Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonypali...

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch the Best of CID episodes:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G3Tw9LL9pT_EQ1yNvFZYBhI

----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3699 - 20 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3699: Tapu Brings Gifts
--------------------------------------------------------
As Tapu enters his house, he experiences nostalgia and tells Jethalal that he used to miss it when he was away for his studies. He responds in a humorous way when Jethalal inquires about his academic pursuits. He gifts Jethalal a wallet and gives Bapuji a shawl while claiming to have gifts for both of them that were concealed in the prank box. He also decides to go door-to-door and inform the Gokuldham members of his hidden gifts. Stay tuned to witness more fun and frolic!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3699, 20 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Shifting to New House |Chennai to Kerala | Meghna Vincent |House shifting
snippet.description:
Namaskaram !
                                                   In this video I share my experience of moving from Chennai to my new home in Kerala. The move was challenging, but with allyour blessings, everything turned out great. I'm excited to share how I organized and arranged my new home, which was a lot of work but worth it in the end.

I'll take you through the process of packing up my belongings, transporting them to my new home, and unpacking and arranging everything. 

Join me on this journey as I settle into my new home in Kerala. Thank you for your support and blessings throughout this exciting and challenging time

Farq Episode 33 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 20th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

We will explore how the key to successful answer writing lies in having a deep understanding of the chapter's story and themes, and how this understanding can help you recall important details and concepts when it comes time to write your answers.

By following the tips and strategies outlined in this video, you will learn how to approach your studies in a more holistic and integrated way, allowing you to build a strong foundation of knowledge that will serve you well in all aspects of your academic and professional life.

So if you're looking to improve your answer writing skills and take your studies to the next level, be sure to check out this video and learn how to unlock the full potential of your own mind!

snippet.description:

Farq Episode 34 Teaser - 20th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3697 - 17 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3697: The Prankster Returns
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu makes a grand entry that surprises everyone. Jetha and Bapuji get really happy after seeing Tapu. Bhide gets a little irritated because of Tapu's mysterious, quirky gifts. Even Iyer complains about the strange robot that he received. Anyway, Tapu Sena celebrates Tapu's entry with a group dance. Sonu, Gogi, and Hans all shake their legs with Tapu and feel extreme joy at their friend's return. Stay tuned to witness more fun and frolic!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3697, 17 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Method (Sabudana vada) ‚Äì
‚Ä¢ Wash the sabudana well, drain the water then add 2-3 tbsp water and cover and soak it for 5-6 hours.
‚Ä¢ After 5-6 hours take soaked sago into a parat / big plate.
‚Ä¢ Grind sabudana on pulse mode for a sec only .
‚Ä¢ Add sabudana into parat or plate and add boiled potatoes and mash and mix well.
‚Ä¢ Then add salt, sugar, red chilly pw, green chilly, crushed peanut pw , cumin, fresh coriander and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Then make flat vadas and deep fry into medium hot oil. 
‚Ä¢ Super Crispy Sabudana vada is ready to serve with chutley. 
Method ( Chutney) ‚Äì

snippet.title: Episode 897 - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Full Episode | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Haar ke jeetne waale ko baazigar kehte hain aur humari Vinny haar manne waalon mein se bilkul nahi hai. But the question is, will RJ Farhan help her find The Winning Secrets?
To know more about Ather, visit: https://www.atherenergy.com

Watch 'The Winning Secrets EP2: Goals are for Losers.' to find out more!

Final Episode releasing on 24th Feb. Stay Tuned!

There may be secrets to winning. But it's no secret that 1 lakh+ riders have been winning commutes, grocery runs, impromptu road trips and more, with Ather. The Ather 450X is new again. For starters, now it's the only scooter in the world* with Google Maps. Get up to 146 km on a full charge. And a top speed of 90 km/h.
